						               													<description>Battles of the American Civil War was the first expansion for the Volley &amp; Bayonet &amp;quot;big battle&amp;quot; miniatures rules.  While most of the rules for the American Civil War were given in the basic V&amp;amp;B rules, the BACW source book ties them together in a more cohesive set.  The BACW book adds rules for multi-day battles and entrenchments, and adds a point system for constructing ad hoc balanced ACW battles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A strategic game (heavily based on GDW &amp;quot;House Divided&amp;quot; rules) is included, allowing players to play a campaign game if they so desire.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Scenarios and orders of battle are included for:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Second Manassas&amp;#10;Antietam&amp;#10;Brandy Station&amp;#10;Gettysburg&amp;#10;Third Winchester&amp;#10;Shiloh&amp;#10;Stone's River (Murfreesboro)&amp;#10;Champion's Hill&amp;#10;Chickamauga&amp;#10;Franklin&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
